{"tid":1017144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國官媒表示今年一季度GDP增速可能降至6%","createTime":"2019-02-11T09:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T12:04:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d741485cd47feb9324289c5fe418d97e664b8659","tid":1017144,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"中國官媒表示今年一季度GDP增速可能降至6%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081390?full=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001081390%3Ffull%3Dy&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=5b4894df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081390?full=y</a><br />\n<br />\n據一家官方報紙報導，今年第一季度，中國經濟增速可能放緩至有記錄以來的最低水平。<br />\n<br />\n「不難判斷，今年我國經濟將繼續承壓，保守估計全年累計增速將落至6.3%左右，當季增速則有可能探至6%，「中國官方新聞社新華社(Xinhua)旗下報紙《經濟參考報》(Economic Information Daily)周一在頭版評論文章中表示。<br />\n<br />\n這一增速將低於2018年第四季度的6.4%&mdash;&mdash;6.4%為中國自全球金融危機以來的最低季度增速&mdash;&mdash;也成為自1990年代初中國開始發布季度經濟數據以來的最低增速。<br />\n<br />\n2018年，中國經濟增速為6.6%，為1990年以來的最低年度增速，1990年時中國曾遭受天安門事件之後國際制裁的衝擊。"},{"pid":"ba6fd82df0c7607b7cb860b6d3fa99b19971e89c","tid":1017144,"uid":42921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"經濟下行, 股市上行, 係咩現象"},{"pid":"d2a81da998b46257cf8bb02a32c0bc131c63876d","tid":1017144,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"迴光返照現象"},{"pid":"381d84c4197375787c4ea8b06bf75174fb3334a5","tid":1017144,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba6fd82df0c7607b7cb860b6d3fa99b19971e89c","tid":1017144,"uid":42921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"經濟下行, 股市上行, 係咩現象"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc37bac6e1d2da91d41e14089d1e9be29930bdcc","tid":1017144,"uid":121146,"like":3,"disli